B.aa0=new A.f(B.w,"Geni\u015f Zaman nedir?",'Geni\u015f Zaman (Present Simple), **d\xfczenli tekrarlanan olaylar**, **kal\u0131c\u0131 ger\xe7ekler** ve **prosed\xfcr kurallar\u0131** i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r.\n\nHavac\u0131l\u0131kta kontrol listeleri, sistem a\xe7\u0131klamalar\u0131 ve ATC prosed\xfcrleri bu zamanda yaz\u0131l\u0131r:\n"The captain **performs** a pre-flight check before every flight."\n"ATC **issues** clearances to all departing aircraft."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.t=new A.nx(1,"rule")
B.a35=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131","**Olumlu:** Subject + **V1** (he/she/it \u2192 +s/es)\n**Olumsuz:** Subject + **do/does not** + V1\n**Soru:** **Do/Does** + Subject + V1?\n\n\u2713 The engine **runs** at full power.\n\u2713 Pilots **do not skip** checklists.\n\u2713 **Does** the aircraft **carry** enough fuel?",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
