B.X5=new A.r("Inspect the brake assembly for wear, cracks, and fluid leakage. Replace any components that do not meet the serviceability limits.","Fren tertibat\u0131n\u0131 a\u015f\u0131nma, \xe7atlak ve s\u0131v\u0131 s\u0131z\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131 i\xe7in inceleyin. Kullan\u0131labilirlik s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131n\u0131 kar\u015f\u0131lamayan par\xe7alar\u0131 de\u011fi\u015ftirin.","serviceability limits")
