B.a9p=new A.f(B.w,"Zamirler neden gereklidir?",'Zamirler, isimlerin yerine ge\xe7erek tekrara d\xfc\u015fmemizi engeller. Havac\u0131l\u0131k ileti\u015fiminde k\u0131sa ve net c\xfcmleler i\xe7in zamiri do\u011fru se\xe7mek kritiktir:\n"The captain completed **his** checklist." (possessive)\n"The ATC cleared **them** for approach." (object pronoun)',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
