B.a8q=new A.f(B.w,"Geni\u015f Zaman nas\u0131l tan\u0131n\u0131r?","Bir c\xfcmlede belirli anahtar kelimeler varsa, fiil b\xfcy\xfck ihtimalle **Present Simple**'d\u0131r. \xd6zellikle s\u0131kl\u0131k zarflar\u0131 (frequency adverbs) ve al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131k belirten ifadeler geni\u015f zaman\u0131n ipucudur.\n\n**Kural:** Soruda zaman ipucu yoksa ve eylem genel bir ger\xe7e\u011fi anlat\u0131yorsa \u2192 Present Simple.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a3Y=new A.f(B.t,"S\u0131kl\u0131k Zarflar\u0131 (Frequency Adverbs)",'| Zarf | S\u0131kl\u0131k | \xd6rnek |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| never | %0 | Pilots **never** skip safety checks. |\n| rarely / seldom / scarcely | %10 | ATC **rarely** approves that route. |\n| occasionally / sometimes | %40 | We **sometimes** divert due to weather. |\n| usually / generally / mostly / often / frequently | %60\u201380 | Aircraft **usually** cruise at FL350. |\n| always / all the time | %100 | The crew **always** completes the checklist. |\n\n**Di\u011fer ipu\xe7lar\u0131:** every day/week/month, timetables, scientific truths, "date back / go back / trace back"',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Vs=new A.r("Pilots never skip the pre-flight checklist.","Pilotlar u\xe7u\u015f \xf6ncesi kontrol listesini hi\xe7 atlamaz.","never")
B.Xr=new A.r("The aircraft sometimes diverts to an alternate due to weather.","U\xe7ak zaman zaman hava ko\u015fullar\u0131 nedeniyle alternatif pistlere sapma yapar.","sometimes")
B.TK=new A.r("The ATIS broadcast updates every hour.","ATIS yay\u0131n\u0131 her saat g\xfcncellenir.","every hour")
