B.a2Q=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131","**K\u0131sa s\u0131fatlar (1-2 hece):** adj + **-er** than / the adj + **-est**\n  \u2192 long \u2192 **longer** than / **the longest**\n  \u2192 safe \u2192 **safer** / **the safest**\n\n**Uzun s\u0131fatlar (3+ hece):** **more** + adj / **the most** + adj\n  \u2192 efficient \u2192 **more efficient** / **the most efficient**\n  \u2192 severe \u2192 **more severe** / **the most severe**\n\n**D\xfczensizler:** good/**better**/best \xb7 bad/**worse**/worst \xb7 far/**further**/furthest",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
