B.a7Q=new A.f(B.w,"Ba\u011fla\xe7lar neden \xf6nemlidir?",'Ba\u011fla\xe7lar, iki c\xfcmleyi veya fikri mant\u0131ksal bir ili\u015fkiyle birle\u015ftirir. Havac\u0131l\u0131k raporlar\u0131nda ve talimatlar\u0131nda c\xfcmleleri do\u011fru ba\u011flamak, bilginin a\xe7\u0131k iletilmesini sa\u011flar:\n"The engine failed **and** the crew declared an emergency."\n"The runway was wet **but** the landing was successful."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.abt=new A.f(B.t,"Temel Ba\u011fla\xe7lar","**Ekleme:** and (ve), also (ayr\u0131ca), both...and (hem...hem de)\n  \u2192 The captain **and** the co-pilot completed the checklist.\n\n**Z\u0131tl\u0131k:** but (ama), yet (oysa), although / even though (kar\u015f\u0131n), while (oysa ki)\n  \u2192 The weather was poor, **but** the flight continued.\n\n**Neden:** because (\xe7\xfcnk\xfc), since (i\xe7in), as (i\xe7in)\n  \u2192 We diverted **because** the destination was below minimums.\n\n**Sonu\xe7:** so (bu y\xfczden), therefore, thus\n  \u2192 Fuel was low, **so** the crew requested priority.\n\n**Ko\u015ful:** if (e\u011fer), unless (e\u011fer...masayd\u0131), provided that\n  \u2192 **Unless** the weather improves, we will divert.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
