B.a5I=new A.f(B.w,"Present Perfect nedir?",'Present Perfect, ge\xe7mi\u015fte ger\xe7ekle\u015fen **ama \u015fimdiye etkisi olan** olaylar\u0131 anlat\u0131r. Havac\u0131l\u0131kta son bak\u0131m durumu, tecr\xfcbe bildirimi ve son durum g\xfcncellemelerinde s\u0131k\xe7a kullan\u0131l\u0131r:\n"The crew **has been** briefed."\n"Engineering **has cleared** the aircraft for departure."\n"Have you **received** the latest ATIS?"',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a4L=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131","**Olumlu:** Subject + **have/has** + V3\n**Olumsuz:** Subject + **have/has not** + V3\n**Soru:** **Have/Has** + Subject + V3?\n\nS\u0131k kullan\u0131lan zaman zarflar\u0131:\n\u2022 **already** (zaten), **yet** (hen\xfcz \u2014 soru/olumsuzda)\n\u2022 **just** (az \xf6nce), **ever/never** (hi\xe7)\n\u2022 **since** (den beri), **for** (s\xfcredir)",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
