B.a8l=new A.f(B.al,"\ud83d\udca1 Present Perfect vs Past Simple",'Tam zaman\u0131 belli ge\xe7mi\u015f \u2192 **Past Simple**\n\u2713 The engine **failed** at 14:32. (belirli zaman)\n\nZaman\u0131 belirsiz veya \u015fimdiye ba\u011fl\u0131 ge\xe7mi\u015f \u2192 **Present Perfect**\n\u2713 The engine **has failed** before. (deneyim, zaman belirsiz)\n\n"We **have cleared** the runway." (\u015fu an haz\u0131r \u2192 etkisi \u015fimdi)\n"The crew **cleared** the runway at 0820." (belirli zaman)',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
