B.aab=new A.f(B.w,"Present Perfect nas\u0131l tan\u0131n\u0131r?","Present Perfect (have/has + V3) belirli anahtar kelimelerle gelir. Bu kelimeleri tan\u0131mak soru \xe7\xf6z\xfcm\xfcnde b\xfcy\xfck avantaj sa\u011flar.\n\n**FIDOW kural\u0131:** For, In (the past), During, Once/Over, While + ge\xe7mi\u015f d\xf6nem \u2192 Present Perfect",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a3C=new A.f(B.t,"Present Perfect Anahtar Kelimeleri","**since** \u2192 belirli bir ba\u015flang\u0131\xe7 noktas\u0131ndan beri\n  \u2192 The aircraft has been grounded **since** Monday.\n\n**for** \u2192 belirli bir s\xfcre boyunca\n  \u2192 The captain has flown **for** twenty years.\n\n**just** \u2192 az \xf6nce\n  \u2192 The crew has **just** received the updated clearance.\n\n**already** \u2192 beklenden \xf6nce ger\xe7ekle\u015fti\n  \u2192 Engineering has **already** inspected the engine.\n\n**yet** \u2192 hen\xfcz (soru/olumsuz c\xfcmlelerde)\n  \u2192 Has the aircraft been refuelled **yet**?\n\n**ever / never** \u2192 hi\xe7 / hi\xe7 olmamak\n  \u2192 Have you **ever** declared an emergency?\n\n**lately / recently / so far / up to now / all my life** \u2192 yak\u0131n d\xf6nem etkisi",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
