B.abL=new A.f(B.w,"Tip 1 Ko\u015ful nedir?",'Birinci Tip Ko\u015ful c\xfcmleleri, **ger\xe7ek ve olas\u0131** durumlar i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r. Sonu\xe7 mant\u0131ksal ve m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr.\n\nHavac\u0131l\u0131kta acil prosed\xfcrler, kural maddeleri ve operasyonel kararlar \xe7o\u011funlukla bu yap\u0131yla yaz\u0131l\u0131r:\n"**If** the oil pressure drops below 40 PSI, **the crew will shut down** the engine."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a6l=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131",'**If** + Present Simple, **will/can/may/must** + V1\n\n\u2713 If the visibility drops below 550m, the crew will execute a missed approach.\n\u2713 If you receive a TCAS RA, you must follow it immediately.\n\u2713 If fuel reaches bingo, the aircraft can divert immediately.\n\n**Dikkat:** if-c\xfcmleci\u011finde "will" kullan\u0131lmaz!\n\u2717 If the weather **will improve**, we will depart.\n\u2713 If the weather **improves**, we will depart.',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
