B.a3M=new A.f(B.w,"Gerund mu, to-infinitive mi?","Bir fiili ba\u015fka bir fiilin nesnesi ya da \xf6znesi olarak kullanmak istedi\u011finde iki se\xe7enek var:\n\u2022 **Gerund** (V-ing): \xf6zne olarak, veya belirli fiillerden sonra\n\u2022 **to-Infinitive**: ama\xe7 belirtmek, veya ba\u015fka belirli fiillerden sonra\n\nHavac\u0131l\u0131k metinlerinde bu yap\u0131lar \xe7ok s\u0131k ge\xe7er: *avoid stalling*, *need to check*, *recommend carrying extra fuel*.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a9l=new A.f(B.t,"Hangi yap\u0131 ne zaman?","**Gerund (-ing) kullanan fiiller:** enjoy, avoid, recommend, consider, suggest, keep, risk, deny\n  \u2192 The crew **avoided flying** through the storm.\n  \u2192 Engineers **recommend checking** torque values.\n\n**to-Infinitive kullanan fiiller:** need, want, decide, plan, agree, refuse, manage, fail\n  \u2192 The captain **decided to divert**.\n  \u2192 The aircraft **failed to climb** above FL200.\n\n**Her ikisini alan fiiller:** like, start, begin, continue, prefer (anlam ayn\u0131 kal\u0131r)\n  \u2192 We started **checking / to check** the systems.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
