B.a63=new A.f(B.w,"Past Continuous nedir?",'Past Continuous (was/were + V-ing), ge\xe7mi\u015fte belirli bir anda **s\xfcrmekte olan** eylemi anlat\u0131r. Kaza soru\u015fturmalar\u0131nda ve durum a\xe7\u0131klamalar\u0131nda kritiktir:\n"The crew **was conducting** the approach **when** the wind shear occurred."\n"At the time of the incident, the aircraft **was climbing** through FL180."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a5R=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131 ve Kullan\u0131m","**Yap\u0131:** Subject + **was/were** + V-ing\n\n**Ne zaman kullan\u0131l\u0131r:**\n1. Belirli bir ge\xe7mi\u015f anda s\xfcren eylem:\n   \u2192 At 14:30, the aircraft **was holding** at FL100.\n2. Bir k\u0131sa eylem uzun eylemle kesi\u015fince:\n   \u2192 The crew **was briefing** when the alert sounded. (uzun + k\u0131sa)\n3. \u0130ki paralel s\xfcregelen eylem:\n   \u2192 While the captain **was flying**, the FO **was computing** fuel.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
