B.U2=new A.r("The cabin crew were serving meals when the seatbelt sign illuminated.","Emniyet kemeri i\u015fareti yan\u0131nca kabin ekibi yemek servisi yap\u0131yordu.","were serving")
B.Ub=new A.r("While the engineers were working on engine 1, a fuel leak was found.","M\xfchendisler 1. motor \xfczerinde \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rken bir yak\u0131t ka\xe7a\u011f\u0131 bulundu.","were working")
