B.a4M=new A.f(B.w,"Edilgen \xc7at\u0131 neden kullan\u0131l\u0131r?",'Edilgen \xe7at\u0131 (Passive Voice), eylemi yapan\u0131 de\u011fil **yap\u0131lan\u0131** \xf6n plana \xe7\u0131kar\u0131r. Havac\u0131l\u0131k prosed\xfcr dok\xfcmanlar\u0131nda ve kaza raporlar\u0131nda \xe7ok yayg\u0131nd\u0131r:\n"The aircraft **was inspected** before departure." (kim yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 de\u011fil, ne yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 \xf6nemli)',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a2I=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131","**am/is/are + V3** \u2192 Present Passive\n  \u2192 The checklist **is completed** before every flight.\n\n**was/were + V3** \u2192 Past Passive\n  \u2192 The fault **was found** during the pre-flight check.\n\n**will be + V3** \u2192 Future Passive\n  \u2192 The engine **will be replaced** next week.\n\n**have/has been + V3** \u2192 Present Perfect Passive\n  \u2192 The aircraft **has been serviced** and is ready.\n\nFail eden ki\u015fiyi belirtmek i\xe7in: **by** + agent\n  \u2192 The report was signed **by** the captain.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
