B.a8_=new A.f(B.w,"Past Perfect nedir?",'Past Perfect (had + V3), ge\xe7mi\u015fteki **iki olaydan \xf6nce olan\u0131** vurgular. Kaza soru\u015fturmalar\u0131nda olaylar\u0131n kronolojik s\u0131ras\u0131n\u0131 netle\u015ftirmek i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r:\n"The crew **had already briefed** the emergency procedure **before** the fault appeared."\n"By the time they reached the runway, the weather **had deteriorated** significantly."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.aaw=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131","**Olumlu:** Subject + **had** + V3\n**Olumsuz:** Subject + **had not** (hadn't) + V3\n**Soru:** **Had** + Subject + V3?\n\nS\u0131k kullan\u0131lan ba\u011fla\xe7lar: **before, after, by the time, already, just, never, when**\n\n\u2713 The aircraft had taxied to the runway before the crew noticed the fault.\n\u2713 By the time maintenance arrived, the leak had stopped spontaneously.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
