B.a8g=new A.f(B.t,"\u0130ni\u015f Tak\u0131m\u0131 Terminolojisi","**Yap\u0131sal bile\u015fenler:**\n\u2022 Shock strut (oleo) \u2014 amortis\xf6r\n\u2022 Torque link \u2014 d\xf6nd\xfcrme ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131\n\u2022 Drag brace / side brace \u2014 geri \xe7ekilme kolu\n\u2022 Wheel well \u2014 ini\u015f tak\u0131m\u0131 yuvas\u0131\n\u2022 Down lock / up lock \u2014 a\xe7\u0131k/kapal\u0131 kilitleme\n\u2022 Squat switch \u2014 yere bask\u0131 \u015falteri\n\n**Fren sistemi:**\n\u2022 Anti-skid system \u2014 kayma \xf6nleme sistemi\n\u2022 Brake pressure \u2014 fren bas\u0131nc\u0131\n\u2022 Brake wear indicator \u2014 fren a\u015f\u0131nma g\xf6stergesi\n\u2022 Hydraulic brake unit \u2014 hidrolik fren birimi\n\n**Ar\u0131zalar:**\n\u2022 Shimmy \u2014 tekerlek titre\u015fimi (yatay d\xfczlem)\n\u2022 Gear not down and locked \u2014 ini\u015f tak\u0131m\u0131 inmi\u015f-kilitli de\u011fil\n\u2022 Hydraulic fluid on gear \u2014 ini\u015f tak\u0131m\u0131nda hidrolik s\u0131z\u0131nt\u0131\n\u2022 Flat spot \u2014 d\xfcz nokta (kayma sonucu tekerlek a\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131)",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
