B.aa9=new A.f(B.w,"Zorunluluk ve tavsiye","Havac\u0131l\u0131kta g\xfcvenlik talimatlar\u0131 ve prosed\xfcrler s\u0131kl\u0131kla **must**, **should** ve **have to** ile ifade edilir. Bu \xfc\xe7 modal'\u0131n fark\u0131n\u0131 bilmek hem s\u0131nav hem u\xe7u\u015f g\xfcvenli\u011fi a\xe7\u0131s\u0131ndan \xf6nemlidir.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a8Q=new A.f(B.t,"Kullan\u0131m Tablosu",'**must** \u2192 i\xe7 zorunluluk, kural / reg\xfclasyon (g\xfc\xe7l\xfc)\n  \u2192 Pilots **must** hold a valid medical certificate.\n  \u2192 Olumsuz: **must not** = yasak!\n\n**have to / has to** \u2192 d\u0131\u015f zorunluluk, ko\u015fullar\u0131n getirdi\u011fi mecburiyet\n  \u2192 We **have to** divert \u2014 fuel is critical.\n  \u2192 Olumsuz: **don\'t have to** = gerek yok (yasak de\u011fil!)\n\n**should / ought to** \u2192 tavsiye, beklenti, \xf6neri\n  \u2192 You **should** review the weather before every flight.\n  \u2192 Olumsuz: **should not** = tavsiye edilmez\n\n\u26a0\ufe0f must not \u2260 don\'t have to:\n\u2022 "You **must not** enter the runway." (kesinlikle yasak)\n\u2022 "You **don\'t have to** wear a jacket." (gerek yok, ama yasak de\u011fil)',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Ue=new A.r("All crew members must wear their ID badges in the security zone.","T\xfcm ekip \xfcyeleri g\xfcvenlik b\xf6lgesinde kimlik kart\u0131 takmal\u0131d\u0131r.","must wear")
B.Xi=new A.r("You should always brief the alternate fuel requirements before departure.","Kalk\u0131\u015ftan \xf6nce her zaman alternatif yak\u0131t gereksinimlerini brifing etmelisiniz.","should always brief")
