B.aDW=new A.j(-266,B.ah,2136,'Translate to Turkish: "A near miss should always be reported, even if no damage occurred."',B.akD,0,B.m,null,null,null)
B.alx=s(["a culture of assigning blame for all safety errors","a culture that encourages reporting by distinguishing between honest mistakes and negligence","a culture where only management decides safety actions","a legal term for fair compensation after accidents"],t.s)
