B.a5s=new A.f(B.w,"Neden devrik c\xfcmle?",'Devrik c\xfcmle yap\u0131lar\u0131 (inversion), **resmiyet**, **vurgu** ve **g\xfc\xe7l\xfc etki** i\xe7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r. ICAO dil testi s\u0131navlar\u0131nda ve resmi havac\u0131l\u0131k belgelerinde s\u0131k\xe7a kar\u015f\u0131la\u015f\u0131rs\u0131n:\n"**Not only did** the crew fail to follow procedures, but they also ignored ATC instructions."\n"**Under no circumstances should** the engine be restarted in flight."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a9j=new A.f(B.t,"Yayg\u0131n Devrik Yap\u0131lar","**Olumsuz zarfl\u0131klar ile:**\n\u2022 Never \u2192 **Never has** such a serious failure occurred.\n\u2022 Not only \u2192 **Not only did** the crew fail, but they also...\n\u2022 Under no circumstances \u2192 **Under no circumstances should** you...\n\u2022 Rarely \u2192 **Rarely do** such errors go undetected.\n\n**Only ile:**\n\u2022 Only after \u2192 **Only after the checklist was completed did** the aircraft depart.\n\u2022 Only when \u2192 **Only when** fuel was critical **did** they divert.\n\n**So/Such ile:**\n\u2022 So serious was the damage that the aircraft was grounded.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Ya=new A.r("Never should a crew member disable a safety system without authorisation.","Bir ekip \xfcyesi, izin almadan hi\xe7bir zaman bir g\xfcvenlik sistemini devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakmamal\u0131d\u0131r.","Never should")
B.Ty=new A.r("Not only did the aircraft lose hydraulic pressure, but the brakes also failed.","U\xe7ak yaln\u0131zca hidrolik bas\u0131nc\u0131n\u0131 kaybetmekle kalmad\u0131, frenler de ar\u0131za yapt\u0131.","Not only did")
B.TU=new A.r("Only after completing the engine fire checklist should the crew assess the damage.","Yaln\u0131zca motor yang\u0131n\u0131 kontrol listesini tamamlad\u0131ktan sonra ekip hasar\u0131 de\u011ferlendirmelidir.","Only after ... should")
B.Yi=new A.r("Under no circumstances should the cargo hold door be opened in flight.","U\xe7u\u015f s\u0131ras\u0131nda kargo kap\u0131s\u0131 hi\xe7bir ko\u015fulda a\xe7\u0131lmamal\u0131d\u0131r.","Under no circumstances should")
