B.a2E=new A.f(B.w,"Ek Soru nedir?",'Ek sorular (tag questions), c\xfcmlenin sonuna eklenerek **onay veya do\u011frulama** amac\u0131 ta\u015f\u0131r. Havac\u0131l\u0131k brifinglerinde ve ekip ileti\u015fiminde "readback" benzeri bir i\u015flev g\xf6r\xfcr:\n"The runway is clear, **isn\'t it?**"\n"You\'ve received the ATIS, **haven\'t you?**"',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a6w=new A.f(B.t,"Yap\u0131 Kural\u0131","**Olumlu c\xfcmle \u2192 Olumsuz tag**\n  \u2192 The aircraft is serviceable, **isn't it?**\n  \u2192 The crew completed the check, **didn't they?**\n\n**Olumsuz c\xfcmle \u2192 Olumlu tag**\n  \u2192 The fuel hasn't been loaded yet, **has it?**\n  \u2192 We can't continue, **can we?**\n\n**Kural:** C\xfcmledeki yard\u0131mc\u0131 fiil tag'de tekrarlan\u0131r.\n\u2022 am/is/are \u2192 isn't/aren't / am I?\n\u2022 was/were \u2192 wasn't/weren't?\n\u2022 have/has \u2192 haven't/hasn't?\n\u2022 will \u2192 won't?\n\u2022 can \u2192 can't?\n\u2022 do/does \u2192 don't/doesn't?\n\u2022 did \u2192 didn't?\n\n**I am \u2192 aren't I?** (\xf6zel kural)",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
