B.a2N=new A.f(B.w,"S\xf6ylem i\u015faretleri nedir?","S\xf6ylem i\u015faretleri (ba\u011fla\xe7lar, ge\xe7i\u015f ifadeleri), c\xfcmleleri ve paragraflar\u0131 **tutarl\u0131 ve ak\u0131c\u0131** bi\xe7imde ba\u011flar. Havac\u0131l\u0131k raporlar\u0131, prosed\xfcr dok\xfcmanlar\u0131 ve ICAO dil testi yazma b\xf6l\xfcm\xfcnde bu ifadeleri do\u011fru kullanmak puan fark\u0131 yarat\u0131r.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a9y=new A.f(B.t,"Kategoriler","**Ekleme:** furthermore, in addition, moreover, also, additionally\n  \u2192 The engine failed. **Furthermore**, the backup system was unserviceable.\n\n**Kar\u015f\u0131la\u015ft\u0131rma/Z\u0131tl\u0131k:** however, nevertheless, despite, although, whereas, on the other hand\n  \u2192 The weather was severe. **However**, the crew managed a safe landing.\n\n**Neden-Sonu\xe7:** therefore, consequently, as a result, thus, due to\n  \u2192 Fuel was critically low. **As a result**, the crew declared an emergency.\n\n**Zaman/S\u0131ra:** initially, subsequently, eventually, finally, at the time, prior to\n  \u2192 **Initially**, the crew attempted a restart. **Subsequently**, they shut down the engine.\n\n**Sonu\xe7/\xd6zet:** in conclusion, overall, to summarise, in summary",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
