B.a4T=new A.f(B.t,"\ud83c\udfc6 \u0130leri Operasyonel Terimler","**EDTO/ETOPS** \u2014 Extended Diversion Time Operations (flying far from alternate airports)\n**RVSM** \u2014 Reduced Vertical Separation Minima (300m / 1,000ft between FL290\u2013FL410)\n**PBN** \u2014 Performance-Based Navigation (RNP, RNAV specs)\n**MNPS** \u2014 Minimum Navigation Performance Specification (oceanic)\n**MEL** \u2014 Minimum Equipment List (approved deferred defects)\n**CDL** \u2014 Configuration Deviation List (approved structural deviations)\n**AOG** \u2014 Aircraft on Ground (urgent unserviceable aircraft)",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
