B.a37=new A.f(B.w,"Ge\xe7mi\u015fteki al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131klar",'**Used to** ve **would**, ge\xe7mi\u015fte tekrarlanan ama art\u0131k yap\u0131lmayan eylemleri anlat\u0131r. Havac\u0131l\u0131k tarihini ve eski prosed\xfcrleri anlat\u0131rken s\u0131k\xe7a kullan\u0131l\u0131r:\n"Pilots **used to** navigate by stars before GPS."\n"Mechanics **would** overhaul engines every 1,000 hours."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a9C=new A.f(B.t,"Fark ve Kullan\u0131m","**Used to + V1** \u2192 ge\xe7mi\u015f al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131klar VE ge\xe7mi\u015f durumlar\n  \u2192 Aircraft **used to** have fewer safety systems. (eski durum)\n  \u2192 The crew **used to** file paper flight plans. (al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131k)\n\n**Would + V1** \u2192 yaln\u0131zca ge\xe7mi\u015f tekrarlayan eylemler (durum i\xe7in kullan\u0131lmaz!)\n  \u2192 The captain **would** always check the weather three times. (al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131k \u2713)\n  \u2192 \u2717 The airport **would** be smaller. \u2192 \u2713 The airport **used to be** smaller.\n\n**Olumsuz:**\n  \u2192 Pilots didn't **use to** have autopilot systems.\n  \u2192 They **wouldn't** depart without a manual weather check.\n\n**Soru:**\n  \u2192 **Did** pilots **use to** navigate differently?",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
