B.a2y=new A.f(B.t,"Havac\u0131l\u0131kta Temel Phrasal Verbs","**take off** \u2192 kalk\u0131\u015f yapmak\n  \u2192 The aircraft **took off** at 0830 UTC.\n\n**touch down** \u2192 inmek, piste de\u011fmek\n  \u2192 We **touched down** on runway 36 at 1420.\n\n**set out** \u2192 yola \xe7\u0131kmak, ba\u015flamak\n  \u2192 The crew **set out** on a 12-hour duty.\n\n**carry out** \u2192 ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirmek, uygulamak\n  \u2192 Engineers **carry out** a 500-hour check.\n\n**hand over** \u2192 devretmek, teslim etmek\n  \u2192 ATC **handed over** the flight to Istanbul Radar.\n\n**run out of** \u2192 t\xfckenmek\n  \u2192 We are about to **run out of** fuel.\n\n**hold up** \u2192 geciktirmek\n  \u2192 The departure was **held up** by a technical fault.\n\n**call off** \u2192 iptal etmek\n  \u2192 The approach was **called off** due to windshear.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
