B.a7_=new A.f(B.w,"Kalk\u0131\u015f \xf6ncesi s\xfcre\xe7","Her u\xe7u\u015fta pilot ve ATC aras\u0131nda ger\xe7ekle\u015fen standart ileti\u015fim s\u0131ras\u0131 \u015f\xf6yledir:\n\n1. **ATIS dinle** \u2014 aktif pist ve hava durumunu \xf6\u011fren\n2. **Delivery'den clearance al** \u2014 rota, transponder kodu, initial altitude\n3. **Ground'dan taxi talimat\u0131 al** \u2014 hangi yoldan piste gidilece\u011fi\n4. **Tower'dan kalk\u0131\u015f izni al** \u2014 \"cleared for takeoff\"",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
