B.a3x=new A.f(B.t,"\ud83d\uddfc Okyanus & Karma\u015f\u0131k Klirans Unsurlar\u0131",'**Oceanic clearance:** "THY1 is cleared to New York JFK via track Bravo, flight level 360, Mach 0.84, squawk 2341"\n\n**Complex enroute:** "THY456, cross TURPO at or above FL280, then direct EMEVI, reduce to Mach 0.80"\n\n**Conditional clearance:** "Behind the departing B777, line up runway 34L and wait"\n\u2014 Always read back: **type of aircraft + condition + instruction**\n\n**SELCAL** \u2014 Selective Calling system for oceanic comms\n**HF** \u2014 High Frequency radio (used in oceanic areas beyond VHF range)',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a5q=new A.f(B.t,"\ud83d\udd04 Bekleme Klirans Dili",'"THY123, hold at TURPO as published, expect approach in 20 minutes"\n"\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026 to the right on the 150 radial, 1-minute legs"\n\n**Key holding terms:**\n\u2022 **Inbound course** \u2014 heading toward the fix during holding\n\u2022 **Outbound leg** \u2014 time/distance spent flying away from fix\n\u2022 **Expect further clearance (EFC)** \u2014 time pilot can expect to leave the hold\n\u2022 **Published hold** \u2014 charted holding pattern; use standard values\n\u2022 "**Left / right turns**" \u2014 direction of turns in the hold',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
