B.abK=new A.f(B.al,"\u2708\ufe0f S\u0131nav \u0130pucu",'S\u0131navlar i\xe7in CAT II/III temel ayr\u0131mlar\u0131:\n\u2022 **DH** = Karar \u0130rtifas\u0131 (radyo altimetre tabanl\u0131, CAT II/III)\n\u2022 **DA** = Karar Y\xfcksekli\u011fi (barometre tabanl\u0131, CAT I)\n\u2022 **RVR** = Pist G\xf6r\xfc\u015f Mesafesi (transmissometre ile \xf6l\xe7\xfcl\xfcr)\n\u2022 Otomatik taksi/fren kullan\u0131labilirse CAT IIIB yakla\u015fma **Karar \u0130rtifas\u0131 olmadan** yap\u0131labilir\n\u2022 LVP, d\xfc\u015f\xfck g\xf6r\xfc\u015fl\xfc kalk\u0131\u015flar\u0131 otomatik olarak iptal etmez \u2014 ayr\u0131 LVT minimumlari vard\u0131r\n\u2022 CAT III i\xe7in "zorunlu g\xf6rsel referans" CAT I\'e g\xf6re **daha azd\u0131r** (yaln\u0131zca pist kenar \u0131\u015f\u0131klar\u0131 yeterli olabilir)',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
